Quick we have to go to the Mun to rescue Jebediah Kerman, lets help Ribnie Kerman go and save Jeb but will we be in time?

Well we continue our Kerbalinian Odyssey and while we go to try and save Jeb we launch some science probes and have a closer look at the mysterious 'Project Iced Kerbal' and see what they are building, hmm 'fascinating'.
